episode: I lost my fantasy baseball matchup last week.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I lost my fantasy baseball matchup last week

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's tough! How are you feeling about it?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I'm disappointed. I  expected to win

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: I understand, that's frustrating.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I feel  like I made too many mistakes

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It's okay, we learn from mistakes.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I always make the same mistakes though

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It's okay; progress takes time.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I hate that I take fantasy so seriously

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It's understandable.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I let it hurt my ego too much

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It's normal to feel that way.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I want to feel like I know more than others

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: I get that.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I spend so much time thinking about it

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It's understandable.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I need to go out more

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That sounds like a good plan.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It would take my mind off of it

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Absolutely.
